<h3 class="sidebar-section">Letters</h3>
<ul class="articles">
<li class="first">
<h4><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/article/why-pasternak-dared/">Why Pasternak Dared</a></h4> <div class="byline"><span class="author-name">Our Readers</span></div> <p><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/article/why-pasternak-dared/"><p>Responses to “The Man Who Dared” by Algis Valiunas</p></a></p>
</li>
<li>
<h4><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/article/what-fdr-could-have-done-for-jewish-children/">What FDR Could Have Done for Jewish Children</a></h4> <div class="byline"><span class="author-name">Our Readers</span></div> <p><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/article/what-fdr-could-have-done-for-jewish-children/"><p>Responses to “‘Children in Europe are Europe’s problem!’” by Robert Slayton</p></a></p>
</li>
<li>
