-Bibi Speech Row: Enough Blame to Go Around, U.S., Germany, and France to Putin: The World Is Too Weak to Stop You, Can Bibi Play Chicken with the Democrats?, Campus Incitement Proves Anti-Zionism Still Equals Anti-Semitism">5</a></td><td><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/2015/02/06/" title="Babylon Deserves UNESCO Protection, Illegal Settlements Must Be Stopped, What Obama Should Have Said at the Prayer Breakfast, The Jobs Report, The Crisis of American Strategy, Give Jordan Drones, Williams and the Myth of the Evening News, Can Iran Be Trusted On Nukes? Can Obama?">6</a></td><td>7</td><td><a href="https://www.commentarymagazine.com/2015/02/08/" title="Netanyahu’s Counterproductive Theatrics, The Crusades Weren’t the Grievance Pundits Believe, Russia Should Pay Reparations After Ukraine, The Race Non Sequitur, Iran and Netanyahu">8</a></td>
